name: GSSP - Good Smell Shit Paradox
description:
That person who loves talk about the poor but is terrified of being part of it. Connoisseur of wines and cheeses but doesn't say good morning to the doorman of the building. That person who criticizes racists but crosses the street when a black man comes his way. These kind of people, it's the kind of people who get in the way of social movements to follow the stupid and unsympathetic reform of their little party.
FUCK0FF.
